2. Objective
Explain that the AI must generate interfaces coherent with the project’s current style, geometry, hierarchy, spacing character, typography roles, and interaction tone.

3. Design philosophy
Merge general UX best practices with the specific visual identity extracted from the project.

4. Non-negotiable style traits
